import Header from '../Header'
import SideBar from '../SideBar'
import {
  HomeContainer,
  SideBarAndContentContainer,
  HomeContentContainer,
  BannerContainer,
  WebSiteLogo,
  BannerText,
} from './StyledComponents'

const Home = () => (
  <HomeContainer>
    <Header />
    <SideBarAndContentContainer>
      <SideBar />
      <HomeContentContainer>
        <BannerContainer>
          <WebSiteLogo
            src="https://assets.ccbp.in/frontend/react-js/nxt-watch-logo-light-theme-img.png"
            alt="website logo"
          />
          <BannerText>Buy Nxt Watch Premium prepaid plans with UPl</BannerText>
        </BannerContainer>
      </HomeContentContainer>
    </SideBarAndContentContainer>
  </HomeContainer>
)

export default Home
